reviewText: It didn't work at all and it must have been faulty.
I HAVE ALWAYS LOVED BODIES IN MOTION, I USE TO HAVE A LOT OF GILAD TAES, NOW WITH EVERYTHING GOING TO DISC'S I DECIDED TO BUY THIS ONE, I LOVE BODIES IN MOTION.
love it! love Gil!!  great workouts.. a little different than some of the older ones so the routines are a little harder.  I really enjoy the challenge
I love these work outs for staying in shape.  They are fun, and build coordination while getting you fit.  Gilad is enthusiastic and funny.  He clearly found his life's calling.

I love Gilad! They may not be a difficult workout but they are nice if you are short on time or you are not for a tough workout. I used to watch these on tv all the time and I'm so glad they are on DVD now.

I have purchased 4 other Gilad DVD's but this is my favorite so far. All 3 workouts are challenging if you give it full effort. Some others DVD's have to much focus on amateurs and bystanders coming into the workout. That to me was a distraction. This is focused and at times intense. The bicycle kick abs are a killer and the inner thigh stuff leaves me SORE. I think you will enjoy the great mountain top scenery and the workout routines. Enjoy!

I purchased Ala Moana Beach, Pupukea and Makapu cliff and these are definitely produced many many years ago (20 years ago maybe?).  Personally, I think they are outdated and I am disappointed because I had thought I was purchasing CURRENT Gilad productions as the production date says 2013.  This is not the case.  I see the fine print on these says they are digitally remastered from series over the last 30 years but I think this should have been declared clearly.  Be warned!
